<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="text-center py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-deep-blue to-gray-900">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About TechSpark</h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Igniting Innovation & Technology</p>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg space-y-8">
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <strong>TechSpark</strong> is a student-driven technical club dedicated to fostering innovation, creativity, and technical excellence among students. The club serves as a platform where passionate minds come together to explore emerging technologies, develop practical skills, and collaborate on exciting ideas and projects.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      At TechSpark, we believe that learning technology should go beyond the classroom. Our goal is to create opportunities for students to gain real-world experience, develop problem-solving skills, and explore their interests in technology through engaging and interactive activities.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission & Vision -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Our mission is to <strong>ignite curiosity and empower students with technical knowledge and hands-on experience</strong>. We aim to build a strong community of learners who are passionate about technology and eager to explore new innovations.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Our Vision</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Our vision is to become a <strong>leading technical community that inspires students to innovate, collaborate, and contribute to the ever-evolving world of technology</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What We Do -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-blue-400">What We Do</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      At <strong>TechSpark</strong>, we focus on creating opportunities for students to explore technology beyond the classroom. Our club regularly organizes a variety of technical activities that encourage learning, innovation, and collaboration.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      We conduct coding challenges, technical competitions, workshops, gaming tournaments, and interactive problem-solving activities that help students develop practical skills and creativity. These activities are designed to strengthen knowledge in areas such as programming, robotics, gaming technology, and emerging technology fields.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Through these initiatives, members get the opportunity to <strong>enhance their technical abilities, work collaboratively in teams, think critically, and gain hands-on experience</strong> that prepares them for real-world challenges.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Join -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-blue-400">Why Join TechSpark</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Joining <strong>TechSpark</strong> provides students with the opportunity to grow both technically and personally in a supportive and innovative environment. Members can improve their skills, learn new technologies, and connect with other passionate tech enthusiasts.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      Being part of the club helps students gain <strong>practical experience, teamwork skills, leadership qualities, and exposure to real-world technical challenges</strong>. It is a place where creativity is encouraged, ideas are valued, and learning continues beyond academics.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Achievements -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-blue-400">Our Achievements</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      TechSpark has successfully organized and participated in numerous technical and interactive initiatives that have engaged students and encouraged innovation. Through these activities, the club has created a vibrant platform for students to explore technology, share ideas, and develop their skills.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
      Over time, TechSpark has built a strong reputation for promoting technical learning and creating an environment where students are motivated to experiment, innovate, and collaborate.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Values -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8">
  <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-blue-400">Our Core Values</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Innovation</strong> – Encouraging creative thinking and the exploration of new technologies and ideas.</li>
      <li><strong>Collaboration</strong> – Promoting teamwork and knowledge sharing to solve problems and build better solutions.</li>
      <li><strong>Learning</strong> – Supporting continuous learning and curiosity in the field of technology.</li>
      <li><strong>Growth</strong> – Helping members develop both technically and personally for future opportunities.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Closing Tagline -->
<section class="container mx-auto p-8 text-center">
  <div class="bg-blue-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <p class="text-2xl italic text-gray-200">
      ⭐ <strong>TechSpark is more than just a club — it is a community of innovators, creators, and tech enthusiasts who come together to learn, build, and spark new ideas.</strong> 🚀
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>